remarks.format:
  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7feee-104">重命名方法参数以使 WMI 客户端具有更好的用户友好名称可能是不方便的。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7feee-104">It might be inconvenient to rename method parameters to present WMI clients with more user-friendly names.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7feee-105">此属性允许您分配用户友好的 WMI 名称，同时保留现有的内部命名约定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7feee-105">This attribute lets you assign user-friendly WMI names while retaining your existing internal naming conventions.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7feee-106">在下面的示例中，integer 参数在内部保持为 i，但会向 WMI 客户端公开为 "值"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7feee-106">In the following example, the integer parameter remains i internally, but will be exposed as "The Value" to WMI clients.</span></span>  
  
```  
[ManagementTask]  
static public int PrintValue([ManagementName("The Value")]int i)  
{  
   Console.WriteLine("The Value is {0:x}", i);  
   return i;  
}  
```
